{"tid":1280703,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［國旗］香港旗設計","createTime":"2019-07-03T05:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T17:00:01.000Z","uid":251001,"like":2,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"406ecbec21238cfe9ac0f299138bae727b71c39b","tid":1280703,"uid":251001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07ZzNWO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07ZzNWO.png&h=55c360f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係小弟自己自創嘅旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旗幟<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">上方藍條</span></span>象徵著香港人擁有<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">自由</span></span>和<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">民主制度</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n下方藍條代表河流/港口，<br />\n和顯示香港嘅水資源對香港人嘅重要性。<br />\n<br />\n中間的雨傘就像一個保護罩一樣<br />\n而雨傘中間有十八顆星 每一顆星代表香港每一個區<br />\n意味著十八個區的香港人都會在雨傘下受到保護<br />\n<br />\n如果大家覺得有咩唔好嘅地方 隨意批評<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d38b2f2b30e47b66f78763ff451a56e8488e67c","tid":1280703,"uid":156592,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b728c2a1992d1d7ac6afc674cc89d144994007","tid":1280703,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:17:14.000Z","msg":"幾有美洲國家feel<br />\n<br />\n🇳🇮🇬🇹🇦🇷🇭🇳🇱🇨"},{"pid":"30fb81c1fd37df88e973aa62381d4d57058a6434","tid":1280703,"uid":7439,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:17:32.000Z","msg":"其實唔好再用遮啦<br />\n好柒"},{"pid":"d697238184149d4cd8d4b52a4e7e8602efc69bfe","tid":1280703,"uid":40908,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:18:47.000Z","msg":"唔好做埋d on9野<br />\n一早講左宜家唔好搞旗住<br />\n集中番宜家要做d咩先啦"},{"pid":"4b89551a6bb84a67125a28ceb2754de5cf78965e","tid":1280703,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:21:11.000Z","msg":"同埋其實用18區做設計係冇咩意義<br />\n因為香港人對各自住嘅區都冇咩歸屬感<br />\n各區之間啲距離同風格相比起美國巴西嗰啲完全唔同 因為都算唔上有好大差異好大不同<br />\n所以冇必要着眼係一個行政單位一粒星咁樣"},{"pid":"3d3db40cba505f7a58a93ab467527fe5e3525306","tid":1280703,"uid":268006,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"406ecbec21238cfe9ac0f299138bae727b71c39b","tid":1280703,"uid":251001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07ZzNWO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07ZzNWO.png&h=55c360f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係小弟自己自創嘅旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旗幟<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">上方藍條</span></span>象徵著香港人擁有<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">自由</span></span>和<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">民主制度</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n下方藍條代表河流/港口，<br />\n和顯示香港嘅水資源對香港人嘅重要性。<br />\n<br />\n中間的雨傘就像一個保護罩一樣<br />\n而雨傘中間有十八顆星 每一顆星代表香港每一個區<br />\n意味著十八個區的香港人都會在雨傘下受到保護<br />\n<br />\n如果大家覺得有咩唔好嘅地方 隨意批評<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:04:56.000Z","msg":"老娘通常只讀不回。今次想真批評。係咪得架？"},{"pid":"f0f667eecc771823e3355aae46f64aa1693459fc","tid":1280703,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:05:34.000Z","msg":"好多星 勁共勁共勁共勁共"},{"pid":"9dcaa378fd4074f866f78e197d415345f683d939","tid":1280703,"uid":268006,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:41:41.000Z","msg":"趁人少講兩咀：<br />\n色：藍白? 撞撐警。兼，呢兩隻色有咩意思？be water?<br />\n構